(161, 'Fluffy Fruit', 'This fruit enables its user to accelerate the growth rate of plants and control them at will. Its user can use it mainly to trap or attack enemies with vines, but also to protect himself from enemy attacks. However, it can only grow plants in environments where vegetation is present.', 'Mosa Mosa no Mi', 'Paramecia', 'https://images.api-onepiece.com/fruits/', 'https://images.api-onepiece.com/fruits/'),
