(165, 'Fruit of the Link', 'This fruit enables its user to transform those he touches into other individuals, copying their appearance, abilities and strength. However, the user cannot transform himself.', 'Kone Kone no Mi', 'Paramecia', 'https://images.api-onepiece.com/fruits/', 'https://images.api-onepiece.com/fruits/'),
