(167, 'Fruit of the Cube', 'It enables its user to transform everything he touches into cubes (soil, ships, humans) and control them. When assembled, these cubes can form more complex structures.', 'Kyubu Kyubu no Mi', 'Paramecia', 'https://images.api-onepiece.com/fruits/', 'https://images.api-onepiece.com/fruits/'),
